    "start_time": 859.32,
    "end_time": 860.0,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 20,
    "text": "、、ありがとうございまし、皆。",
    "start_time": 1662.0,
    "end_time": 1668.16,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 21,
    "text": "、もうYouTubeのチャットの方でも、泣けるとか、拍手してくれたりと、",
    "start_time": 1669.4,
    "end_time": 1676.0,
    "speaker": "",
    "role": null,
    "corner": null
  },
  {
    "id": 22,
